{"comments":"Atomic state management inspired by Jotai/Recoil\n\nAtoms are the smallest unit of state. They can be read, written, and\nsubscribed to. Derived atoms compute values from other atoms.\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.State.Atom as Atom\n\n-- Create an atom\ncountAtom <- Atom.atom 0\n\n-- Read value\ncount <- Atom.get countAtom\n\n-- Update value\nAtom.set countAtom 5\nAtom.modify countAtom (_ + 1)\n\n-- Subscribe to changes\nunsubscribe <- Atom.subscribe countAtom \\newValue ->\n  Console.log $ \"Count changed to: \" <> show newValue\n\n-- Derived atoms\ndoubledAtom <- Atom.derived countAtom (\\n -> n * 2)\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"An atom holds a single piece of state\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":["Representational"],"typeArguments":[["a",null]]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[87,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/State/Atom.purs","start":[81,1]},"title":"Atom"},{"children":[],"comments":"A read-only view of an atom (for derived atoms exposed publicly)\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":["Representational"],"typeArguments":[["a",null]]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[90,47],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/State/Atom.purs","start":[90,1]},"title":"ReadOnlyAtom"},{"children":[],"comments":"A store holds multiple atoms and enables snapshots\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[95,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/State/Atom.purs","start":[93,1]},"title":"AtomStore"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create a new atom with an initial value\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"a","kind":null,"skolem":null,"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"a","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"con